    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eij jelle pee tahm Awim/ \nun dabbu man no turrenes diwi \ndischannus Ahſifchus/ tad fataiſi-\nfchu es tehſ tawam Tehwam/ \npar gardeem Wirrumeem/ itt \nka wiꞥſch eezeeni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Untew buhſ tawam Teh-\nwam preeſcha zelt/ ka wiꞥſch \nehd/ un tero swehtt/ pirms ka \nwiꞥſch mirſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jehkabs us \nRebekku fawn Mahti: Reds/ \nEsaivs mans Brahlis irr weens \nſpatwaitsch Wihrs/ un es eſmu \npliks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jaſchu mans Tehws man \naptaustihs/ tad buhſchu es wiꞥ-\nna Azzis itt ka Krahpneeks/ un \nusweddischu pahr mann Lahstu/ \nun ne Swehtumu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija winna Mahte \nus winnu: lat tawi Lahsti us \nmannim paleek/ mans Dehis: \nklaust tikbai mannai Balsi/ un \neij/ dabbu man tohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nogahje wiꞥſch/ un \nnehme/un atneffe fawai Mahtei/ \nun winna Mahte fataiſija gar-\ndus Wirrumus/ itt ka winna \nTehws tohs eezeenija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Rebekka nehine Eesa-\nwa/ fawa wezaka Dehla krahp-\nnakas Drehbes/ kas tai Namna \nbija/ un apwilke taḥs Jehkabam \nfawam jaunaḳum Dehlam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un taḥs Kaſlenu Ahdas \naplikke ta apkahrt winna Roh-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un winna detwe tohs gar\ndus Wirrunus un to Maifi/ k \nwinna bij fataiſiſſi/ Jehkaba fu \nwa Dehla Rohka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nahze pee faw \nTehwa:un fazzija: MansTehws \nun tas fazzija: ſche es eſmu/ ka \neffi tu mans Dehls?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Jehkabs u \nfawn Tehwu: Es eſmu Eesaw \ntaws Pirmdsimcajs/es eſmu da \nrijis/ itt ka tu us man effi run \nnajs/ Zellees/ luhdsams/ apſe \ndeeg/ un ehd no manna Meddiju \nma/ ka mann tawa Dwehfe \nsivehti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Ihsaảks u \nfawn Dehtu/ kas ir tas/ ka tu \ntik drihs effi atraddis/ ma \nDehts? un tas fazzija: ta \nKUNGS taws DEews li \nman to fastapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Ihsaảks u \nJehkabu: Mahz jelle ſchur/ ka \ntew aptaustu/ mans Dehls/ a \nrig tu effi tas pats mans Deh \nEesaws/ jeb ne.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jehkabs peegahje p \nfawa Tehwa Ihsaảka/ un wiꞥ \naptaustija to/ un wiꞥſch fazzij \nta Bals irr Jehkaba Bals/ b \ntahs Rohkas irr Eesaiva Rohka\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch ne pasinne t \njo winna Rohkas bija spaſi-\nnas/ itt ka winna Brahta Ef \nwa Rohkas/ un wiꞥſch sweh \nja to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija: Efi \n"
    }
  ],
